import discord
from discord.ext import commands
import json
from datetime import datetime
from datetime import timedelta


bot = commands.Bot(command_prefix='!!', description="This is a Helper Bot")

@bot.command()
async def ping(ctx):
    await ctx.send('pong')

@bot.command()
async def add(ctx,inv_amt,inv_days,ret_x,user_id):
    user = ctx.message.author.id
    if user == 792675560056422410:
            ret_amt = float(inv_amt) * float(ret_x)
            dat  = datetime.today().strftime('%d-%m-%Y') 
            gf = float(inv_days)
            enddate = (datetime.now() + timedelta(days=gf) ).strftime('%d-%m-%Y')
            embedVar = discord.Embed(title="New Invested Added", description="Invested By "+ f"<@{user_id}>", color=0xfffff)         
            embedVar.add_field(name="Invested Date", value=f"**{dat}**")
            embedVar.add_field(name="Invested Amount", value= "**"+ inv_amt + " Rs"+ "**", inline=True)
            embedVar.add_field(name="Return Date", value= "**"+ enddate + "**", inline=False)
            embedVar.add_field(name="Invested Amount", value= "**"+ str(ret_amt) + " Rs"+ "**", inline=True)
            embedVar.set_footer(text="Bot Made By: NotDefined#5467")
            embedVar.set_thumbnail(url="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/975724783385849978/982272233089159208/5ad662f0b184739863addc175c5189f5.png")
            await ctx.channel.send(embed=embedVar)
            obj = {'Invested Amount': inv_amt, 'Invested Date': dat , 'Return Date': enddate , 'Return Amount': ret_amt}    
            encoded = json.dumps(obj)
            with open('data.txt', 'a') as f:
                f.write(encoded +'\n')
    else:
        await ctx.send("**You Are Not Authorized To Use This Command**")






@bot.event
async def on_ready():
    await bot.change_presence(activity=discord.Activity(type=discord.ActivityType.listening, name="Tirth"), status=discord.Status.dnd)
    print('My Ready is Body')


bot.run('OTgyMjUxODc4MDU2MzQ1NjQx.GNY29U.WpSYOTbvPFDNJX4D4k9CK0XiZPxNRwa1MUTuNk',bot=True)
